'''Bokang Phelane''' ni umukinnyi wa filime ukomoka muri Lesotho  no muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]], <ref>https://consumercouncil.africa/insights/meet-the-artist-bokang-phelane/</ref> akaba producer n'umwanditsi wa filimi . <ref>https://tshimologong.joburg/events/broke-ass-web-series-masterclass/</ref>

== Ubuzima n'uburere ==
Phelane yavukiye i [[Maseru]], muri [[Lesoto|Lesotho]] . Yize amashuri yisumbuye mu mujyi yavukiyemo, nyuma akomereza muri kaminuza ya Monash muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] aho yakuye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts muri Psychology . <ref>https://taggedonline.co.za/lifestyle-entertainment-content/exclusive-blood-psalms-elevating-african-stories-to-epic-proportions/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2016, Phelane rwaravuzwe muri series comedy televiziyo,''Single Guys,'' gukina uruhare, "Fezeka". <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt8718886/</ref> Yagaragaye kandi mu biganiro bya televiziyo, ''Shuga'', byasohotse mu 2018, aho yakinnye nk'umugore wa Andile "Fezeka". <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt2577388/fullcredits/cast?ref_=m_ttfc_3</ref>

Muri Nyakanga 2017, yakinnye nka ''Pula'' muri Season 1 ya telenovela yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]],''Keeping Scores'', yerekanwe kuri SABC2. <ref>https://www.tvsa.co.za/shows/viewshowseasons.aspx?showId=3454&season=1</ref> Yakinnye nka "Lily" mu rurimi rw'Abazulu Sci-Fi TV-seriyeri, ''Emoyeni (Netflix)'', yasohotse ku ya 22 Nyakanga 2018. <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt8686452/</ref> Yagaragaye mu mvugo y’ururimi rwa Sotho, ''Isipho Sothando'', yerekanwe muri Werurwe 2020 <ref name="Is">https://www.dstv.co.za/whats-on/news/articles/12-shows-that-shine-a-light-on-mzansi-s-brilliant-storytelling/</ref> ndetse no muri ''Ho Kena Ho Eona,'' yerekanwe muri Mata 2020 <ref>https://www.dstv.co.za/whats-on/news/articles/what-to-watch-on-mzansi-magic-in-march/</ref> haba kuri DSTV. Niwe uyoboye urukurikirane rw'ibiganiro bya televiziyo nyafurika, ''Blood Psalms'', azasohoka hamwe na ba producer Showmax na Canal + International mu 2021, akina nka "Zazi", umwamikazi w'ingimbi ukabije. <ref>https://stories.showmax.com/originals/blood-psalms/</ref> <ref>https://www.multichoice.com/media/news/multichoice-joins-forces-with-canalplus-to-co-produce-african-mythology-epic-blood-psalms/</ref> <ref>https://www.techafricanews.com/2020/09/02/showmax-announces-two-coproductions-megan-fox-action-movie-and-canal-epic-in-ancient-africa/</ref>

